'''奶头'''也叫'''乳头'''，是[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]][[乳房|乳房]]中央突起的圆柱状部分，比[[乳晕|乳晕]]和乳房要硬。雌性哺乳动物的乳头有[[哺乳|哺乳]]功能，[[母乳|乳水]]會從[[乳腺管|乳腺管]]經由乳头分泌，餵養嬰兒<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefreedictionary.com/nipple|title=nipple|publisher=|accessdate=4 August 2017|via=The Free Dictionary|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213121323/https://www.thefreedictionary.com/nipple|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{sfn |Hansen|2010|p=80}}。乳水可能是因為乳头受力而流出，也可能是因為[[平滑肌|平滑肌]][[肌肉收缩|收缩]]而流出。乳头周圍的組織稱為[[乳晕|乳晕]]，其顏色會比乳房顏色要深一些<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tabers.com/tabersonline/view/Tabers-Dictionary/762857/1/nipple&ti=0|title=nipple - Taber's Online|website=www.tabers.com|accessdate=12 August 2017|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109001717/https://www.tabers.com/tabersonline/view/Tabers-Dictionary/762857/1/nipple%26ti%3D0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。人类乳头是重要的[[性感帶|性感帶]]。乳头由紧密的[[平滑肌|平滑肌]]和[[结缔组织|结缔组织]]组成。平滑肌环行或放射状排列，当遇到[[性刺激|性刺激]]或[[力學|力學]][[刺激|刺激]]时，平滑肌收缩，可使乳头变硬凸起<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://archive.is/P9NZl|title=乳房愛撫技巧大公開|last=|first=|date=2017-03-05|work=|newspaper=臉紅紅|accessdate=2017-03-05|archive-date=2018-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180804221420/http://archive.is/P9NZl|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在許多文化中，會將女性的乳头「[[性化|性化]]」<ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=http://sociologytoolbox.com/social-construction-of-the-body/|title=Social Construction of the Body: The Nipple|publisher=sociologytoolbox.com|author=Todd Beer|date=2015-05-12|accessdate=2015-05-16|archive-date=2016-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116020737/http://sociologytoolbox.com/social-construction-of-the-body/|dead-url=no}}</ref>或「視為性目標的一部份，以其實體特徵及性感程度來評斷」<ref name=Dewar>{{cite web | last = Dewar | first = Gwen | title = The sexualization of girls: Is the popular culture harming our kids? | url = http://www.parentingscience.com/sexualization-of-girls.html | website = parentingscience.com | publisher = Parenting Science | date = October 2012 | accessdate = 2019-04-03 | archive-date = 2019-04-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190401215249/https://www.parentingscience.com/sexualization-of-girls.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 大小 ==
正常乳头两侧对称，表面粉红色或棕色。男性大部份黑色居多，且有毛。女性乳头圆柱状部分直径一般为0.8-1.5厘米，高出乳晕平面约1.5-2厘米。异常发育导致的凸瘤状增生与管状突出增生被称为[[乳头过大|乳头过大]]。

== 数量 ==
乳头数量跟繁殖力（一胎产仔数）相关，多为偶数，从2个到18个不等。例如灵长类、羊、马有两个乳头；牛有4个乳头；猫有8个乳头。但[[北美负鼠|北美负鼠]]有13个乳头，其中12個圍成一個圓形及1個在中間<ref>{{Cite web |author=Jerry Jackson |title=with the Wild Things |publisher=Florida Gulf Coast University |accessdate=2008-01-14 |url=http://digitalcollections.fiu.edu/wild/transcripts/possums1.htm |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130323001102/http://digitalcollections.fiu.edu/wild/transcripts/possums1.htm |archivedate=2013-03-23 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |author=Mary Stockard |title=Raising Orphaned Opossums (''Virginianus carolinensis'') |year=2005 |url=http://www.awrc.org/Baby%20Opossums.htm |accessdate=2008-01-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100701012225/http://www.awrc.org/Baby%20Opossums.htm |archivedate=2010-07-01 }}</ref>。如果有人有3-4个乳头，都会被称为[[副乳|多乳症]]。

== 構造 ==
乳头周遭表面凹凸不平有点像菜花状，女性乳头有6-9个输送乳汁的[[乳腺|乳腺]]开口和数量不等的[[皮脂腺|皮脂腺]]开口， 皮脂腺开口一般不会超过20个。乳头由乳头顶、乳头颈和乳头底组成。乳头颈部受年龄和生育哺乳的生理影响，一般少女乳头颈部短小，上小下大，有点像锥柱体；生育哺乳后的乳头颈部变大变长，便于哺乳。同时，[[妊娠|妊娠]]后受到体内[[雌激素|雌激素]]和[[孕激素|孕激素]]增加的影响，乳头颜色也渐渐加深。

雄性哺乳动物包括人类男性也有乳头，乳头比较短小。而且乳腺管退化没有哺乳或其它功能，但亦是性敏感部位。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://tw.mensuno.asia/article/detail/170/%E7%94%B7%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%B3%E9%A0%AD%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9F|title=男人的乳頭究竟有什麼用？|accessdate=2020-05-27|language=zh-hant|author=|date=|work=|publisher=|format=|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202094911/https://tw.mensuno.asia/article/detail/170/%E7%94%B7%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%B3%E9%A0%AD%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9F|dead-url=no}}</ref>

